                            <comment id="38336" author="pjones" created="Tue, 8 May 2012 15:32:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Roger&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We have only tested up to 24TB LUNs for 1.8.x releases. If you need larger LUN sizes it would be recommended to use a 2.1.x release&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Regards&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
